{
  "texts": [
    "The task is to classify the nature of a diagnosis from a colposcopy.",
    "The time series represent the change in intensity values of a pixel region through a sequence of digital colposcopic images obtained during the colposcopy test that was performed on each patient included in the study.",
    "The ElectricDeviceDetection data set (Bagnall et al. 2020b) contains formatted image data for the problem of detecting whether a segment of a 3-D X-Ray contains an electric device or not.",
    "The data originates from an unsupervised segmentation of 3-D X-Rays.",
    "The data are histograms of intensities, not time series."
  ]
}